<plot>A hybrid documentary/ game show series in which a pair of contestants are blindfolded, flown by private jet to an unknown corner of the earth and dumped there with only $100 to work out where in the world they are and then get themselves back to London. Drop locations were as diverse a Northern Quebec in the depth of winter and the Sahara Desert in Africa. Each 2 part 90 minute film charts the adventures of three teams dropped near each other and intercuts their stories as they race against each other to be first back to Nelson's Column in London and win a substantial cash prize.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?343465</url></doc>
